Italy Outlook Revised to Negative by Standard & Poor’s; Ratings Affirmed

-- B y   V i v e k   S h a n k a r
-- 
2011-05-20T22:27:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-20/italy-outlook-revised-to-negative-by-standard-poor-s-ratings-affirmed.html
Italy’s credit outlook was revised to
negative from stable by Standard & Poor’s Ratings Services,
which affirmed the country’s A+/A-1+ sovereign credit ratings.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
